prompt:
Create a 4-day Red Sea diving mini-itinerary for an intermediate diver staying in Dahab in November. Include only recreational no-decompression dives, and assume the diver is already certified and diving with a reputable local dive center. Return the plan as JSON with this exact structure:
{
  "base_location": string,
  "month": string,
  "experience_level": string,
  "days": [
    {
      "day": integer,
      "dives": [
        {
          "site_name": string,
          "approx_max_depth_m": number,
          "entry_type": "shore" | "boat",
          "notable_features": [string]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
Do not include any medical, legal, or training advice in the JSON or outside it.
